recipe winter melon soup canh bí_đao danang cuisine homereciperecipe winter melon soup canh bí_đao recipe winter melon soup canh bí_đao by helen_le published september 2014 500 winter melon 17.6 oz 200 shrimps oz spring onion cilantro chopped use pair of_scissors to trim off the tip of_the head_and_and some of_the front legs then peel off the shell you just have to peel the upper part of_the shrimp then just_hold and_press the_tail and_the lower part of_the shell will just slide off or you can use everything including the_skin and_and the head in a_mortar and_pestle add the shrimps shallot tsp_salt and_pound it slightly then add tsp fish sauce tsp pepper peel and_cut the winter melon into inch pieces remove the soft part in the center with the seeds you want to trim off the edges that when you slice it its slice of_winter melon will not have sharp corner slice into thickness of_about an_inch in a_saucepan add tsp of vegetable_oil and_fry some of_the shallots until fragrant then add the_shrimps and_stir fry on high heat until they turn orange then add liter of cups of_hot water adding hot water will help to reduce the fishy smell of the_shrimps and_also prevent overcooking them season the soup with your taste add about tsp salt_and tsp chicken stock then add the winter_melon and_bring the soup to a_boil again winter melon cooks very fast as soon as the soup boils again just turn off the heat if you use chayote or kohlrabi you_can cook little longer transfer to a_large bowl_and garnish with some chopped spring onion or cilantro mcf tiêu mcf dầu thực_vật tôm bóc vỏ lưng nguyên giã tôm củ hành tím ướp mcf muối mcf mắm mcf_tiêu công_thức nấu canh_bầu su_su su_hào bí_đao gọt vỏ chẻ trái to chẻ ruột tỉa cạnh cắt lát bí_đao góc nhọn cắt lát dày 4-5 mm chút dầu nồi phi_hành thơm tôm xào lửa màu cam lít sôi bí đun_sôi trở_lại sôi giúp tôm đỡ_tanh nấu bí_đao mau chín sôi tắt lửa bí chín dần nấu su_su su_hào đun mềm bát rắc hành_ngò canh bi_daorecipesoupwinter melon soup
